// Vernacular — Debug configuration
//
// LOCAL DEVELOPMENT ONLY.
//
// • Replace the placeholder values below with your real Supabase credentials
//   BEFORE building locally for the first time.
// • DO NOT commit real secrets to a public repo. If this repo becomes public,
//   add this file to .gitignore and distribute via a secure channel.
// • In CI, write these values into the xcconfig at build time using secrets
//   (e.g., GitHub Actions / Xcode Cloud environment variables).
//
// Supabase anon keys are safe to ship in client apps (they're meant to be public),
// but we still avoid committing them to reduce the blast radius if rotated.

SUPABASE_URL = https:/$()/YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY = YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
